Install react-i18next for internationalization (i18n): This is a powerful and flexible internationalization library for React.
npm install react-i18next i18next

Ensure each page and component is using the useTranslation hook to dynamically update text based on the selected language.
When you select a different language in the Header.tsx, all the components will automatically update the text according to the translations provided in your JSON files (en.json, es.json, etc.).
The t('key') function will replace the static text with the appropriate translation